OL,3,CRobin Swann pressed on 'playing
OL,4,Cpolitics' with health service
OL,6,FThe Health Minister Robin Swann has
OL,7,Frepeated that he is prepared to vote
OL,8,Fagainst the current Stormont budget,
OL,9,Feven if it leads to his resignation.
OL,11,FAnswering questions at the Stormont
OL,12,FHealth Committee Mr Swann has also
OL,13,Fbeen accused of playing politics with
OL,14,Fthe health service.
OL,16,FThe committee hearing took place as
OL,17,Fjunior doctors confirmed they will
OL,18,Fstage two further 48 hours walkouts
OL,19,Fover the next few weeks.
