OL,6,FHe was commenting after recently
OL,7,Fqualified doctors announced plans for
OL,8,Ftwo 48-hour walkouts in May and June
OL,9,Fafter pay talks with Mr Swann and his
OL,10,Fdepartment broke down.JThe planned
OL,11,Factions will take place from 7am on
OL,12,FWednesday May 22 to 7am on Friday May
OL,13,F24 and from 7am on Thursday June 6 to
OL,14,F7am on Saturday June 8.JJunior doctors
OL,15,Fin Northern Ireland took strike action
OL,16,Ffor the first time in March, staging a
OL,17,F24-hour walkout that affected
OL,18,Fhospitals and GP surgeries.JThe strike
OL,19,Faction was called after 97.6% of
OL,20,Fjunior doctors balloted by their
OL,21,Funion, BMA Northern Ireland, voted in
OL,22,Ffavour of industrial action.JThe BMA
OL,23,Fhas called for a commitment to a full
OL,24,Fpay restoration to 2008 levels,
